body:
@MarcoFalke Hmm! That warning icon *used to be text* - and I don't recall users encountering this problem back when it was... maybe changing it to an icon was a terrible mistake.

@dabura667 If normal users need to touch the console, something is terribly wrong.

@sipa Creating a new address is already a pop-up; I agree adding a noticeable warning there would be an improvement.
